.grid-container.centered
	h3.text-center Add Bundle
	form(method="post" ng-submit="submit()" name="addBundleForm")
		label Title
			input(type="text", ng-model="title" placeholder="Enter bundle title" name="title" required)
			.validation(ng-if="loginForm.title.$dirty" ng-messages="loginForm.title.$error")
				.message(ng-message="required") Try again, a title is required
		label URL
			input(type="url", ng-model="url" placeholder="URL" name= "url" required)
			.validation(ng-if="loginForm.url.$dirty" ng-messages="loginForm.url.$error")
				.message(ng-message="required") We do need a title though

			button.button-auth.expand(type="submit" ng-disabled="addBundleForm.$invalid") Submit
			a(href="#" ng-click="cancel()") Close